
Overview of noun abomination

The noun abomination has 3 senses (no senses from tagged texts)
                                  
1. abomination -- (a person who is loathsome or disgusting)
2. abhorrence, abomination, detestation, execration, loathing, odium -- (hate coupled with disgust)
3. abomination -- (an action that is vicious or vile; an action that arouses disgust or abhorrence; "his treatment of the children is an abomination")
